Welcome to `FTown Of Salem` `2Hackmud Edition`!
This is an interface guide. Game guide: `1http://town-of-``1salem``1.wikia``1.com/wiki/Getting_Started`

`FLobby`
To queue up for a game, use `Nqueue`: `Vtrue`.
The game will start automatically when 15 players queue up.
If you are the host, you can start the game early, once there are at least 4 players, you can manually start the game with `Nstart`: `Vtrue`.

`FDay`
To vote, use `Nvote`: `0<player #>`
